name: Spinferno: Pinball From Hell! (Canceled)
blurb: Spinferno is the craziest, Dante-inspired, hellishly exciting voodoo pinball game on the planet! Create your victim & get revenge!

rewards.reward: Eternal Condemnation:\r\nYou have a special place in Hell and you deserve some recognition! Your name will appear in Spinferno on the "List of the Condemned!"
NEW REWARD!! LIMITED AMOUNT Purgatory: You're not quite in heaven, but you're not in hell either. Your glorious gift is just the download of Spinferno when the project is complete.

The Vestibule:\r\nYou've committed to entering the vast, nefarious  Circles of Hell! In addition to the recognition on the "List of the Condemned", you've also earned a download of Spinferno when it's complete.

Circle I-Limbo:\r\nYou've escaped the Vestibule and have made it to the great unknown. You'll receive the special gifts reserved for those in lower circles of hell, plus 3 custom WALLPAPERS for your desktop and your phone featuring art by Spinferno artist, Bernard Gumz!
"Vote Obama...Straight to Hell!": Backers of this level will receive a custom "Vote Obama...Straight To Hell!" t-shirt with art illustrating POTUS poised about the fires of Eternal Funishment!

"Vote Romney...Straight to Hell!": Backers of this level will receive a custom "Vote Romney...Straight To Hell!" t-shirt with art illustrating the 2012 Republican candidate for President strapped to the Wheel of Doom!

Circle II-The Lustful:\r\nWe can tell you really want this!  Along with the rewards from all the previous levels, your donation reserves a special, limited edition Spinferno POSTER with art by Bernard Gumz!

Circle III-The Gluttonous:\r\nYou enjoy life's indulgences, so don't be ashamed! To make your stay in this eternal circle with Cerebus less infernal, we're going to give you a T-SHIRT with custom art inspired by Spinferno!
Circle IV-The Greedy:\r\nYou gotta have everything, huh? In addition to all the previous gifts, you'll get the special Spinferno Refrigerator MAGNET PLAYSET!  Make Spinferno levels everywhere!

Circle V-River Styx (Anger):\r\nYour anger is so powerful, you've been damned to the river! Spinferno backers will receive all previous mentioned rewards and will receive the custom created Spinferno COMIC BOOK!

Circle VI-City of Dis (Heresy):\r\nOnly ONE soul that can endure this countryside of pain and anguish. In this circle you will get the official CONTRACT FOR YOUR SOUL! And we'll throw in the Spinferno DEMON BABY seen in our infamous commercial! Lucky bastard!

Circle VII-The Violent:\r\nFor those souls that suffer from fits of rage or brutality!  You'll get: your name on the "List of the Condemned", three WALLPAPERS for your phone and computer, one Spinferno POSTER, one Spinferno T-SHIRT, one Spinferno MAGNET PLAYSET, one Spinferno themed COMIC BOOK, the official CONTRACT FOR YOUR SOUL and a "Special Damnation!" credit in the Spinferno Game. Damn, that's a lot!

Circle VIII-Malebolge (Fraud):\r\nEw! This region is reserved for panderers and seducers. You get everything The Violent level does, plus a custom Spinferno-inspired AVATAR  beside your name in the "Special Damnation!" credit, and now be on the official list of Game Producers! Fancy you!

Circle IX-Cocytus (Traitors):\r\nAs a traitor entering this final circle of Hell, we know you need something enticing. Get all of the goodies of The Fraudulent level, plus the chance to have your custom avatar featured somewhere in the game, and you'll get to Beta Test Spinferno!

Exit From Hell:\r\nOnly few can accomplish the feat of climbing down Lucifer's shaggy body, struggling through the tombs, and making their way out of purgatory to once more see the stars! For your efforts and generous pledge, you'll receive everything the dirty Traitors level, plus your avatar as a SELECTABLE character in the game (though it may be hidden at first), and the fantastic HELL IN A HANDBASKET kit, featuring a smorgasbord of Hell Related goodies! You're gonna love it! Or hate it.
